    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with no major issues, providing a reliable driving experience. While the interior and exterior show some minor signs of normal use, such as small surface scratches or slight wear on the upholstery, the car remains very clean and presentable. All major systems are functioning as they should, making this an excellent choice for anyone seeking a dependable and well-cared-for vehicle.",
